    Scope and Contents
HOME SCHOOLING PROJECT 
Hutchins discusses her experiences with home schooling: children's reaction to home schooling, curriculum of the Christian Liberty Academy, legalities, support groups, advantages, disadvantages, and reasons for home schooling, opposition to the program, and incorporating the roles of mother and teacher. 1 tape, 57 mins., 19 pp. 
Interview by Linda Moore, 1990 
